name: Dead Branch (Doppelganger)
description: You can use it to summon Doppelganger in Guild Fortress. Attention! The wild Boss and Boss summoned by Dead Branch have the same attributes, and they cannot be damaged and looted for 2 hours because of the operation of "Channel Teleporter". The monster summoned will survive for up to 10 minutes.
